<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">LoL...I gotta respond again

To the person who said that game designers/programmers don't want their software hacked. LoL your proally right but you know that they KNOW it is gunna get hacked in some shape or form in the future. Who knows you may have a bootlegged (HACKED) copy of some software somewhere on your computer!

I think the whole idea of player policing is a JOKE! Oh he KSed me, well he dupes!! How do I know I was there...I mean COME ON! Reporting another player is LAME! I understand this is a rebuke coming from a PREVIOUS guide/GM. But realize how unbalanced this game has become! 1st they handed my FUCKING fire pet to anyone who wants it. Yes, it is a LOW level pet but it’s a pet none the less! WTF is up with that?!?! They handed my Bandages to Warriors and such! WTF!! My defining abilities handed out like they were playthings! Here is my response to the Cheating and player policing part of this thread! GO PISS ON YOURSELF AND BURN IN HELL!!

Fix the game BEFORE you decide that, OH SHIT we need another expansion!!

BTW I am still pissed as hell that any caster can now summon a fire element! And any warrior type can summon bandages! Fuck lets just make one class that fits all Verant! Screw all our chances of getting in groups!

The way I see it is I am totally justified because the dumb ass programmers should have foreseen this. Tell me this, have you EVER seen a NPC jump. I am not talking about falling off the top of a building, I am talking about JUMP, in place or what ever! NO! So what gives you the idea that if you place a rock which users can jump from to a ledge that the NPC can follow?? Easily solved but Verant is just a bunch of dumb asses. SOLUTION: Place a RAMP instead of a LEDGE! This way PPL can still group and pull to here and not have to worry about wall spawns and such just another pull spot! WOW THAT WAS FUCKING HARD AS HELL!!

And to D23 and his “If you were a warrior, you 'd not have a chance, at least you could gate as a caster” Shit. Well that’s Great I bet you play A LOT. Anyone knows that a twink warrior could solo here EASY!! I saw a 31 warrior taking on 4 targets UNASSISTED! No he was no cheating he was THROUGHLY TWINKED though! Twinking is as bad IF NOT WORSE than cheating! EXAMPLE: you camp the Skele jester for the supposed 40 to 80 hours it takes to get an IBC. While you are camping it you see a level 4 shm come in with full Jaundiced armor and a IBC wouldn’t you be a bit ticked? I bet so!

Ok enough ranting. I consider what I did OK and none will change my mind. The screw the game more every patch and all I hope is that this “Class balancing” thing goes as planned.


GUARDIANX</TEXTAREA>
